---
title: Herby Beef Koftas with Jewelled Couscous & Yoghurt
description: Couscous is a great side that loves to soak up flavour. We’re jazzing it up tonight with flavourful stock, lemon zest and currants so it truly holds its own against these Middle Eastern-inspired beef and parsley koftas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-koftas-pine-nut-currant-couscous-65442f29.jpg
